\begin_inset Formula $K_{H}=\left\{ 0\right\} \times S^{1}$
\end_inset

 oder anders formuliert 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
K_{H} & = & \left\{ \left(0,\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\exp\left(i\xi_{2}\right)\right):\quad\xi_{2}\in\mathbb{R}\right\} .
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
